query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS canadian_grid_carbon_data (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    provinceCode VARCHAR(5) NOT NULL,
    provinceName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    emissionFactor DECIMAL(6,4) NOT NULL,
    renewablePercent DECIMAL(5,2) NOT NULL,
    carbonRating ENUM('low', 'medium', 'high') NOT NULL,
    dataYear INT NOT NULL,
    dataSource VARCHAR(255),
    isActive INT DEFAULT 1 NOT NULL,
    createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    INDEX idx_province_year (provinceCode, dataYear),
    INDEX idx_active_data (isActive)
);
